// TypeUid is an enum, and the following values are allowed.
// 300200 - Unknown
// 300201 - Logon: A new logon session was requested.
// 300202 - Logoff: A logon session was terminated and no longer exists.
// 300203 - AuthenticationTicket: A Kerberos authentication ticket (TGT) was requested.
// 300204 - ServiceTicketRequest: A Kerberos service ticket was requested.
